############################################################
# Unified Environment Template (authoritative)
#
# Policy
# - Do NOT commit real secrets. This template is for local copies (.env).
# - Provider API keys should be stored securely in ~/.config/artemis/env
#   via `make artemis-setup` and validated with `make env.check`.
# - This single template replaces historical variants:
#     â€¢ .env.example, .env.sophia.example, .env.mcp.example (deprecated)
#
# Usage
#   cp .env.template .env
#   # edit values as needed for local dev
#
# Note: Docker compose services may also read env_file: .env
############################################################

# ====================
# GENERAL / APP
# ====================
